ers for every discipline.\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 828, \"end\": 834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9995937764278602, \"rank\": 0.0003185946754903194, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only a handful\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 859}, {\"ngram\": \"nations\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 870}, {\"ngram\": \"qualified riders\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"every discipline\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only Great Britain has been able to enter the maximum number of athletes in track, MTB and road.\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 1016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 925, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.8386786527592274, \"rank\": 0.19194859636043515, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_women's_national_field_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1003, \"end\": 1006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mountain_bike\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.048362065097693e-23, \"text\": \"MTB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mountain_bike\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mountain_bike\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the maximum number\", \"from\": 962, \"to\": 980}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 984, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1001}, {\"ngram\": \"road\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Getting Canada to the same stage as a powerhouse Olympic performer like GB is a result of hard work by the riders, eight coaches and supporting staff, and financial support from Sport Canada.\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1208, \"ent