"us\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1397}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest levels\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1427}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The one thing that is really unique about Canada is that we do not have the numbers that some other countries do in our development pipeline.\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1572, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1473, \"end\": 1479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9995937764278602, \"rank\": 0.0003185946754903194, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The one thing\", \"from\": 1431, \"to\": 1444}, {\"ngram\": \"the numbers\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1514}, {\"ngram\": \"some other countries\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1540}, {\"ngram\": \"our development pipeline\", \"from\": 1547, \"to\": 1571}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cycling is not the culture in Canada, hockey is in the culture, for sure.\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1603, \"end\": 1609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9995937764278602, \"rank\": 0.0003185946754903194, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cycling\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1580}, {\"ngram\": \"the culture\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1599}, {\"ngram\": \"hockey\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1617}, {\"ngram\": \"the culture\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So often, we are selecting riders from a very small talent pool.\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1711, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"riders\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1680}, {\"ngram\": \"a very small talent pool\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's really important that we make sure that they can stay in the sport for a while, and that we are maximising the talent that we do have.\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1854, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1786}, {\"ngram\": \"the talent\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a compact group, so we have to have good relationships with everybody.\\\"\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1931, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a compact group\", \"from\": 1860, \"to\": 1875}, {\"ngram\": \"good relationships\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1929}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are very excited about it,\\\" Proulx said of maxing out the track cycling team.\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 2014, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Proulx\", \"from\": 1965, \"to\": 1971}, {\"ngram\": \"the track cycling team\", \"from\": 1991, \"to\": 2013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To my knowledge, this is the first time Canada has ever done that.\", \"from\": 2015, \"to\": 2082, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2056, \"end\": 2062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9995937764278602, \"rank\": 0.0003185946754903194, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my knowledge\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2031}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2055}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We hoped to qualify the maximum number of spots, but it was never a guarantee until the very last event.\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2187, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the maximum number\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2121}, {\"ngram\": \"spots\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2130}, {\"ngram\": \"a guarantee\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2160}, {\"ngram\": \"the very last event\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before Milton [the last Nations Cup], we were optimistic and hopeful but 