\": \"exchanges\", \"from\": 6399, \"to\": 6408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every training session includes video analysis, power analysis, and aero testing.\\\"\", \"from\": 6425, \"to\": 6507, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Every training session\", \"from\": 6425, \"to\": 6447}, {\"ngram\": \"video analysis\", \"from\": 6457, \"to\": 6471}, {\"ngram\": \"power analysis\", \"from\": 6473, \"to\": 6487}, {\"ngram\": \"aero testing\", \"from\": 6493, \"to\": 6505}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mental preparation also plays a significant role in Canada's strategy.\", \"from\": 6509, \"to\": 6579, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6561, \"end\": 6567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.9995937764278602, \"rank\": 0.0003185946754903194, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mental preparation\", \"from\": 6509, \"to\": 6527}, {\"ngram\": \"a significant role\", \"from\": 6539, \"to\": 6557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have invested in the mental performance game, creating a performance environment that is light, bright, and clear,\\\" Proulx noted.\", \"from\": 6580, \"to\": 6713, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mental performance game\", \"from\": 6601, \"to\": 6628}, {\"ngram\": \"a performance environment\", \"from\": 6639, \"to\": 6664}, {\"ngram\": \"Proulx\", \"from\": 6700, \"to\": 6706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our mental performance coach, Sharlen Hoar, works with the athletes and coaches to create environments that bring out the best in people.\", \"from\": 6714, \"to\": 6852, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our mental performance coach\", \"from\": 6715, \"to\": 6743}, {\"ngram\": \"Sharlen Hoar\", \"from\": 6745, \"to\": 6757}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 6770, \"to\": 6782}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 6787, \"to\": 6794}, {\"ngr